Available Tools: get_conversion_rate | track_event | get_funnel_data | get_goal_completions
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "event_name": "string", "funnel_id": "string", "from_date": "string", "to_date": "string" }
Response Schema: { "event": "string", "total_events": number, "unique_users": number, "conversion_rate": number, "funnel_steps": [{ "name": "string", "completions": number }] }
---
Question: What was the success rate for the password reset flow during the security update last Tuesday?
